Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:28.26,ed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFB4EF8&\3c&HFFFFFF&}現在也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:30.93,ed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFB4EF8&\3c&HFFFFFF&}我們無法預知明天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:33.26,ed,,0,0,0,,就算是我 總有一天
